# OctoFit Tracker Frontend Environment Variables
# Copy this file to .env and fill in the values

# GitHub Codespace name (automatically set by GitHub Codespaces, or set manually)
# For local development, comment out or set to empty
# For GitHub Codespaces, this should be automatically set as: REACT_APP_CODESPACE_NAME
# Example: REACT_APP_CODESPACE_NAME=my-codespace-name

# If using local development, the API will default to http://localhost:8000
